# URLs to skip during lychee link-checking.
# Add entries here only after confirming they're reachable from a normal
# browser - this file suppresses false positives, not real broken links.
# Format: one regex per line (matches anywhere in the URL).

# DNS blocklist sources - large files / slow hosts that time out under HEAD/GET
^https://raw\.githubusercontent\.com/hagezi/dns-blocklists/
^https://small\.oisd\.nl/?$

# Doc sites occasionally rate-limited from CI runners
^https://kubernetes\.io/docs/
